message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.1">
    <title>AI Code Store - CyberPunk</title>
    <style>
        /* reset base */
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'system-ui', 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica, sans-serif';
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
        background: radial-gradient circle at center, #0d0c0d 0%, #1a0033 100%;
        color: #f0f0ff;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

        /* cyberpunk main */
        .card {
        max-width: 960px;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(10, 10, 20, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px #0ff2, 0 0 20px #0ff4;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        transition: 0.3s;
        margin: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: pulse 2s infinite alternate;
    }

    .card::before,
    .card::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -0%;
        left: 0%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #f0ff00, #0ff, #f0f, #0ff);
        opacity: 0.1;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .card>* {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #f0ff;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #f0f, #0ff, #ff0;
        -webkit-backclip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        font-weight: 900;
        filter: drop-shadow 0 0 10px #0ff;
    }

    .sub-p {
        color: #b0b0ff;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0ff8;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .card-item {
        background: #0a0a0a80;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.2rem;
        transition: 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff2;
        backdrop-filter: blur( 4px);
    }

    .card-item:hover {
        background: #0ff1;
        border-color: #f0f;
        transform: scale 1.02;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #f0f;
    }

    .card-item h3 {
        color: #f0f;
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #f0f;
    }

    .price {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0ff;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #0ff;
        color: #0a0a0a;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
        border: 2px solid #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff, 0 0 20px #f0f;
        transition: 0.2s;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: none;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #0ff, #f0f;
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        transform: scale 0.9;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #f0f, 0 0 40px #0ff;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #f0f, #0ff;
        color: #fff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #000;
    }

    .form-group {
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    input, textarea, select {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.1rem 0.2rem;
        background: #0a0a0a;
        border: 1px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #f0f;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        outline: none;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #f0f;
    }

    label {
        color: #b0b0ff;
        display: block;
        margin: 0.5rem 0 0.2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    textarea {
        min-height: 6rem;
        resize: vertical;
    }

    .pop {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: #00000080;
        backdrop-filter: blur( 4px);
        z-index: 100;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .pop.active {
        display: flex;
    }

    .pop-box {
        background: #0a0a0a;
        border: 2px solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 2.5rem 3.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px #0ff, 0 0 20px #f0f;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 90%;
        animation: flick 0.3s;
    }

    .pop-box h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #0ff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff;
    }

    .pop-box p {
        color: #b0b0ff;
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .close {
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid #f0f;
        color: #f0f;
        padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .close:hover {
        background: #f0f;
        color: #000;
    }

    footer {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: #b0b0ff;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #0ff4;
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    }
